Interface IpmiResponse

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IpmiCommand, IpmiPayload, Wireable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractIpmiConfigurationParametersResponse, AbstractIpmiResponse, AbstractIpmiSimpleResponse, ChassisControlResponse, CloseSessionResponse, GetChannelAccessResponse, GetChannelAuthenticationCapabilitiesResponse, GetChannelCipherSuitesResponse, GetChannelInfoResponse, GetChassisCapabilitiesResponse, GetChassisStatusResponse, GetDeviceIdResponse, GetFRUInventoryAreaInfoResponse, GetLANConfigurationParametersResponse, GetSDRRepositoryInfoResponse, GetSDRResponse, GetSELAllocationInfoResponse, GetSELInfoResponse, GetSensorReadingResponse, GetSensorThresholdResponse, GetSOLConfigurationParametersResponse, GetSystemRestartCauseResponse, ReadFRUDataResponse, ReserveSDRRepositoryResponse, SetSessionPrivilegeLevelResponse, UnknownIpmiResponse

    public interface IpmiResponse
extends IpmiCommand
    An IPMI response. An IPMI response has a IpmiCompletionCode, which some implementations consider to be part of the header, but is a part of the response body according to the spec.
    See Also:
